txt.en: You should deliver the items you collected to Tordoron in Echad Uial.
<rgb=#FF00FF>These items may be found by defeating foes in Imlad Morgul instances. Different instances will yield different types of items.</rgb>
Some needed secondary supplies may be found in Imlad Morgul.
'You have returned with the items I asked of you? You have my thanks.'

'While you are out there helping our efforts, we are in need of some lesser resources that are difficult to find.\n\n'If you come across any Morgul plaster or treated dowels, will you gather them for us? Our crafters have been asking for these items in particular.'

Tordoron's guide to finding secondary resources:

Gath Daeroval - the Shadow-roost: crafter's steel, worn trinkets
Gorthad Nûr - the Deep-barrow: deep-lichen, smoothed stones
Eithel Gwaur - the Filth-well: deep-lichen, smoothed stones
Harrowing of Morgul: crafter's steel, worn trinkets
Ghashan-kútot - the Hall of Black Lore: Morgul plaster, treated dowels
Bâr Nírnaeth - the Houses of Lamentation: Morgul plaster, treated dowels
